data.description: 3 bedroom 2 bath ADORABLE home undated throughout . Hardie Board siding for excellent durability and insulation with mature Pecan Trees. Convenient location to downtown, schools and shopping and pride and ownership in neighborhood. Beautiful Wood tones laminate flooring in  living area and kitchen and carpet in bedrooms. Step down to cozy Large add on master suite and bath and separate from extra bedrooms with access to backyard and carport. Lots of  areas for storage and well spaced kitchen featuring stainless appliances, tile backsplash and beautiful wood cabinetry with family size dining open to living area. Separate utility room for washer and dryer off kitchen. Fenced in backyard with convenience from side door of the home with additional COVERED parking with alley access.  Updated window screens, Levolor blinds and foam insulation in attic for comfortable temperatures and savings on utilities.  Walk in to this home and it's MOVE IN READY!
